  "description": "Greatest common divisor of 48 and 18",
  "source": "int main() {\n    int a = 48;\n    int b = 18;\n    while (b != 0) {\n        int t = a;\n        while (t >= b) {\n            t = t - b;\n        }\n        a = b;\n        b = t;\n    }\n    return a;\n}\n",
